---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SectionDivider from '../components/SectionDivider.astro';
import Icon from '../components/Icon.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Membership | The Parlour — The World's Most Exclusive Society of Magic"
  description="Membership in The Parlour is a sacred privilege, passed down through generations of master conjurers. Only those who demonstrate unwavering dedication to the craft and the highest moral character are considered."
  keywords="exclusive magic club membership, San Diego magician society, private magic club, elite magic society, San Diego magic membership, secret magic society"
  ogUrl="https://www.parloursociety.org/membership"
  ogImage="https://www.parloursociety.org/image/hero-membership.jpg"
>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section content-hero content-hero-membership">
        <div class="content-container">
            <h1>Membership</h1>
            <p class="lead">A privilege, not a right</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Who May Petition — Full Width -->
    <section class="content-info">
        <div class="content-container">
            <h2>The Admission Process</h2>
            <div class="content-row">
                <div class="content-col content-col-full">
                    <div class="content-details-card">
                        <h3>Who May Petition</h3>
                        <p>Since time immemorial, The Parlour has existed in the shadows — a lineage of master conjurers passing the flame from one generation to the next. Membership is not something one applies for lightly. It is a calling, recognized by those already within, and extended only to individuals whose devotion to the art is beyond question.</p>
                        <p>We seek practitioners who have dedicated years — often decades — to the mastery of their discipline. Whether your art lies in close-up conjury, grand illusion, mentalism, or theatrical presentation, what matters is not the breadth of your repertoire but the depth of your commitment. The Parlour values character and integrity as highly as technical brilliance. Every member is a guardian of secrets that have been entrusted to this society across centuries.</p>
                        <p>A referral from an existing member carries great weight, though the Council may consider exceptional candidates who petition directly. Admission is never guaranteed. Many petition. Few are chosen.</p>
                        <p><em>Those who belong, know. Those who seek to join must prove they are worthy of the secrets within.</em></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How Admission Works — Full Width Below -->
    <section class="location-details">
        <div class="content-container">
            <div class="content-row">
                <div class="content-col content-col-full">
                    <div class="content-details-card">
                        <h3>How Admission Works</h3>
                        <p>The path to membership is deliberate and exacting — a process refined over generations to ensure that every soul admitted into The Parlour is worthy of the trust, the knowledge, and the brotherhood that awaits within.</p>
                        
                        <div class="content-row content-mt-medium">
                            <div class="content-col content-col-full">
                                <div class="expectation-item">
                                    <span class="emoji-icon"><Icon name="step-1" /></span>
                                    <div>
                                        <h4>Submit Your Petition</h4>
                                        <p>Complete the formal petition with details about your experience, your disciplines, and what draws you to the art. A referral from a current member strengthens your case considerably.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="content-col content-col-full content-mt-medium">
                                <div class="expectation-item">
                                    <span class="emoji-icon"><Icon name="step-2" /></span>
                                    <div>
                                        <h4>Council Review</h4>
                                        <p>The Council convenes in private to review each petition with the gravity it deserves. If your submission demonstrates genuine dedication and alignment with our values, you will be summoned for a private audience.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="content-col content-col-full content-mt-medium">
                                <div class="expectation-item">
                                    <span class="emoji-icon"><Icon name="step-3" /></span>
                                    <div>
                                        <h4>Private Invitation</h4>
                                        <p>Qualified candidates are invited to attend a single gathering as our guest — an opportunity to witness The Parlour firsthand, and for our members to take your measure.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="content-col content-col-full content-mt-medium">
                                <div class="expectation-item">
                                    <span class="emoji-icon"><Icon name="step-4" /></span>
                                    <div>
                                        <h4>Demonstration of Craft</h4>
                                        <p>Candidates present a brief demonstration of their art before the Council. This is not a test of perfection — it is a window into your soul as a practitioner. We seek passion, originality, and an unmistakable connection to the craft.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                </div>

                            <div class="content-col content-col-full content-mt-medium">
                                <div class="expectation-item">
                                    <span class="emoji-icon"><Icon name="step-5" /></span>
                                    <div>
                                        <h4>Initiation</h4>
                                        <p>Upon acceptance, new members undergo the sacred initiation rite — a tradition unchanged since the founding of the society. You will swear an oath of secrecy, contribute the initiation offering, and be formally welcomed into the brotherhood of The Parlour.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="content-mt-medium cta-mobile-center"><a href="#" class="content-btn open-contact-form">Submit Your Petition</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Advancement & Dedication -->
    <section class="content-info">
        <div class="content-container">
            <h2>The Path of Ascension</h2>
            <div class="content-row">
                <div class="content-col content-col-full">
                    <div class="content-details-card">
                        <p>Membership in The Parlour is not a transaction — it is a lifelong covenant. From the moment of initiation, every member embarks on a path of continuous growth, deepening their mastery and their bond with the society.</p>
                        <p>Within The Parlour, members ascend through the ranks not by title or wealth alone, but through a confluence of forces that have governed our order since its inception: demonstrated mastery of the magical arts, years of devoted tenure, mentorship of those who follow, financial stewardship of the society's legacy, and an unwavering dedication to the values upon which The Parlour was founded.</p>
                        <p>Advancement is never requested. It is recognized — observed quietly by the Council and bestowed when the time is right. Those who rise do so because their commitment speaks louder than any petition ever could. They become the keepers of our deepest secrets, the mentors of the next generation, and the guardians of a tradition that stretches beyond living memory.</p>
                        <p><em>The Parlour does not create masters. It reveals them.</em></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Member Privileges -->
    <section class="what-to-expect">
        <div class="content-container">
            <h2>Member Privileges</h2>
            <div class="content-row">
                <div class="content-col content-col-two-thirds content-offset-col">
                    <div class="expectation-list">
                        <div class="expectation-item">
                            <span class="emoji-icon"><Icon name="masks" /></span>
                            <div>
                                <h4>Private Gatherings</h4>
                                <p>Exclusive monthly sessions behind closed doors — world-class performances, intimate lectures, and master workshops conducted by practitioners whose names are known only within these walls</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="expectation-item">
                            <span class="emoji-icon"><Icon name="books" /></span>
                            <div>
                                <h4>The Vault</h4>
                                <p>Access one of the most closely guarded collections of magical knowledge in existence — rare manuscripts, forbidden techniques, and centuries of arcane wisdom passed down through the society</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="expectation-item">
                            <span class="emoji-icon"><Icon name="chain" /></span>
                            <div>
                                <h4>Master Mentorship</h4>
                        <p>Study under accomplished masters who have dedicated their lives to the art — inheriting knowledge that cannot be found in any book or purchased at any price</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="expectation-item">
                            <span class="emoji-icon"><Icon name="stage" /></span>
                            <div>
                                <h4>Performance Stage</h4>
                                <p>Present your art before the most discerning audience in the world — fellow masters who understand the invisible labor behind every impossible moment</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="expectation-item">
                            <span class="emoji-icon"><Icon name="lock" /></span>
                            <div>
                                <h4>The Inner Sanctum</h4>
                                <p>Join a confidential network of the world's finest practitioners — a brotherhood bound by oath, united by craft, and shrouded in secrecy since the society's founding</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <section class="attending-info">
        <div class="content-container">
            <h2>Do You Belong?</h2>
            <div class="content-row content-align-center">
                <div class="content-col content-col-full">
                    <div class="attendance-info" style="text-align: center; max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto;">
                        <p>The Parlour has endured for generations because it has never compromised on who it admits. We do not seek numbers. We seek the exceptional — those rare individuals whose passion for the art burns with an intensity that cannot be taught, only recognized.</p>
                        <p>If you have spent years honing your craft in solitude, if you have felt the pull of something greater than performance, if you believe that magic is not merely entertainment but an ancient and sacred art — then perhaps The Parlour has been waiting for you.</p>
                        <p>The path begins with a single step. Submit your petition, and let the Council decide if your journey leads here.</p>
                        <p class="content-mt-medium cta-mobile-center"><a href="#" class="content-btn open-contact-form">Submit Your Petition</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
   
    <SectionDivider type="wave" />
</Layout>
